nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL DEPRESSION ELEVEN-E FORMS WELL SOUTHWEST OF THE SOUTHERN TIP OF BAJA CALIFORNIA...
summary: ...TROPICAL DEPRESSION ELEVEN-E FORMS WELL SOUTHWEST OF THE SOUTHERN TIP OF BAJA CALIFORNIA... As of 11:00 PM HST Sat Aug 30 the center of Eleven-E was located near 14.4, -122.3 with movement W at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
